{"lemma":"زَلَّةٍ","slug":"زَلَّةٍ","root":"ز.ل.ل","root_slug":"ز-ل-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/ز-ل-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n17949","n17950","n17951"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B2%D9%8E%D9%84%D9%8E%D9%91%D8%A9%D9%8D"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"slip, lapse, oversight","examples":[{"text":"زَلَّةُ لِسَانٍ","english":"slip of the tongue"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"dyspnoea, shortness of breath","tags":["uncountable"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/zal.la/","/zul.la/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n17949","headword_ar":"زَلَّةٌ","root":"zl","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A slip"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, * K) in mud, or in speech; a subst. from 1 meaning as expl. in the first sentence of this art.; (S, K:) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zil~iylaY","text_ar":"زِلِّيلَى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S: [but this latter is mentioned by Lh and in the K as an inf. n.:])"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a slip,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lapse;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a fault, a wrong action, a mistake,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an error;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, K;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a sin,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"crime;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, * TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a fall into sin"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"crime."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Evr","text_ar":"عثر"},{"kind":"text","text":".) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zal~a Alr~ajulu","text_ar":"زَلَّ الرَّجُلُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zal~apF qabiyHapF","text_ar":"زَلَّةً قَبِيحَةً"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The man"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made a foul slip;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fell into the commission of a disapproved,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hateful,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"foul, act;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"committed an exorbitant, an abominable,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a foul, mistake:"},{"kind":"text","text":"whence the trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naEuw*u biA@ll~`hi mino zal~api AlEaAlimi","text_ar":"نَعُوذُ بِا@للّٰهِ مِنْ زَلَّةِ العَالِمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"We seek protection by God from the slip of the learned"},{"kind":"text","text":"man]: and the well-known saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zal~apN AlEaAlimi zal~apu AlEaAlami","text_ar":"زَلَّةٌ العَالِمِ زَلَّةُ العَالَمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The slip of the learned"},{"kind":"text","text":"man"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"is the slip of the world at large"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A benefit,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"good action;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, * K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zul~apN","text_ar":"زُلَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a gift."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A feast,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"repast, that is prepared for guests."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, O, Msb.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ait~axa*a fulaAnN zal~apF","text_ar":"اِتَّخَذَ فُلَانٌ زَلَّةً"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one made,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"prepared, a feast for guests"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Lth, O, Msb.) Hence, (Lth, TA,) it is also a name for"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Food that is carried from the table of one's friend"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"relation:"},{"kind":"text","text":"a word of the dial. of El-'Irák: (Lth, Msb, K:) or in this sense it is a vulgar word, (K, TA,) used by the common people of El-'Irák (TA.) And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EurosN","text_ar":"عُرْسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A marriage-feast"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (ISh, Az, Msb, K.) So in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kun~aA fiY zal~api fulaAnK","text_ar":"كُنَّا فِى زَلَّةِ فُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"We were at the marriage-feast of such a one"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (ISh, Az, Msb, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","Lth","TA","Msb"]},{"entry_id":"n17950","headword_ar":"زُلَّةٌ","root":"zl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zal~apN","text_ar":"زَلَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".       -A2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A straitened state of the breath"},{"kind":"text","text":"[unless"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aln~afasi","text_ar":"النَّفَسِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"be a mistranscription for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aln~afos","text_ar":"النَّفْس"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the soul,"},{"kind":"text","text":"which I think not improbable]. (K.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n17951","headword_ar":"زِلَّةٌ","root":"zl","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Stones:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"smooth stones:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zilalN","text_ar":"زِلَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["K"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}